{"name":"Fleance Flycatcher","size":"medium","type":"Humanoid","tag":"Andradoran","alignment":"NG","hitDice":"5","armorName":"studded leather","shieldBonus":0,"natArmorBonus":5,"otherArmorDesc":"12","speed":"30","burrowSpeed":"0","climbSpeed":"0","flySpeed":"0","hover":false,"swimSpeed":"0","customHP":false,"customSpeed":false,"hpText":"27 (5d8 + 5)","speedDesc":"30 ft.","strPoints":"10","dexPoints":"16","conPoints":"8","intPoints":"18","wisPoints":"12","chaPoints":"14","blindsight":"0","blind":false,"darkvision":"0","tremorsense":"0","truesight":"0","telepathy":0,"cr":"5","customCr":"1 (200 XP)","customProf":2,"isLegendary":false,"legendariesDescription":"[MON] can take 1 villain action, choosing from the options below. Only one Villain action option can be used at a time and only at the end of another creature's turn. [MON] regains spent villain actions at the start of its turn.","isLair":false,"lairDescription":"When fighting inside its lair, the spy can invoke the ambient magic to take lair actions. On initiative count 20 (losing initiative ties), the spy can take one lair action to cause one of the following effects:","lairDescriptionEnd":"The spy can't repeat an effect until they have all been used, and it can't use the same effect two rounds in a row.","isMythic":false,"mythicDescription":"If the spy's mythic trait is active, it can use the options below as legendary actions for 1 hour after using {Some Ability}.","isRegional":false,"regionalDescription":"The region containing the spy's lair is warped by the creature's presence, which creates one or more of the following effects:","regionalDescriptionEnd":"If the spy dies, the first two effects fade over the course of 3d10 days.","properties":[],"abilities":[{"name":"Master of Intrigue","desc":"[MON] has proficiency with the disguise kit, the forgery kit, and dice.\n\nAdditionally, [MON] can unerringly mimic the speech patterns and accent of a creature that he has heard speak for at least 1 minute, enabling him to pass yourself off as a native speaker of a particular land, provided that he knows the language."},{"name":"Sneak Attack (1/Turn)","desc":"[MON] deals an extra 7 (2d6) damage when he hits a target with a weapon attack and has advantage on the attack roll, or when the target is within 5 ft. of an ally of [MON] that isn't incapacitated and [MON] doesn't have disadvantage on the attack roll."}],"actions":[{"name":"Shortsword","desc":"_Melee Weapon Attack:_ [DEX ATK] to hit, reach 5 ft., one target. _Hit:_ [DEX 1D6] slashing damage."}],"bonusActions":[{"name":"Cunning Action","desc":"On each of its turns, [MON] can use a bonus action to take the Dash, Disengage, Hide, or Help action. This help action has a range of 30ft."}],"reactions":[{"name":"Uncanny Dodge (1/day)","desc":"When [MON] is hit with an attack roll he can use his reaction to halve the damage."}],"legendaries":[],"mythics":[],"lairs":[],"regionals":[],"sthrows":[{"name":"dex","order":1},{"name":"int","order":3}],"skills":[{"name":"deception","stat":"cha"},{"name":"history","stat":"int","note":" (ex)"},{"name":"insight","stat":"wis"},{"name":"investigation","stat":"int","note":" (ex)"},{"name":"perception","stat":"wis"},{"name":"persuasion","stat":"cha"},{"name":"stealth","stat":"dex"}],"damagetypes":[],"specialdamage":[],"conditions":[],"languages":[{"name":"Aire","speaks":true},{"name":"Common","speaks":true},{"name":"Dwarvish","speaks":true},{"name":"Orc","speaks":true},{"name":"Thieve's Cant","speaks":true}],"understandsBut":"","shortName":"","pluralName":"","doubleColumns":false,"separationPoint":4,"damage":[]}